          "Write imperative workflow steps that can be executed in order.",
          "State what the module is done when instead of relying on implied completion."
        ],
        "advisory_notes": [
          "Keep the module narrow and composable with other routed modules.",
          "Avoid duplicating repository-wide rules that already live in AGENTS.md."
        ]
      },
      "llm_guidance_mode": "advisory",
